Author: MyDietIsPureTea
Text: My friend talks about how she has porridge for breakfast, and then chickpeas for snack, and then a sandwich for lunch- and THEN dinner?! And she’s still somehow skinnier than I am??!! I seriously don’t know how that happens. Maybe the air in my damn house is super caloric, or some other voodoo bullshit

Author: sioclip
Text: same goes with tall people. ugh
